names.fullName: Emilin1 links TGF-beta maturation to blood pressure homeostasis.

attributeList.attribute: Radio-receptor binding assays was carried out using monolayers of HEK293T cells transfected with HA-tagged type II TGF-beta; Receptor expression plasmid in the presence of a GPI-anchored EMI-domain. 125I-labeled TGF-beta1 (20 pM) was added to transfected cells and washed; the bound ligand was crosslinked with DSS and then immunoprecipitated with anti-HA antibody. Detection of TGF-beta1 was by autoradiography and that of EMi domain was by western blotting.
